aces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7500b090cfa3974461fb43aed3b241c2c0e611e4","tid":1301041,"uid":49669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T06:55:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af1c5d706126d62290fc0973d84bb6a12eabfb53","tid":1301041,"uid":273803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T07:05:44.000Z","msg":"轉頭出個簡報俾各位巴打"},{"pid":"6bf095f1fe718412eef01f6a27907d4565467f6f","tid":1301041,"uid":6833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T07:10:00.000Z","msg":"全部保皇狗?"},{"pid":"f7eeb8b1fcebada716004c1482b2dc92e5368bec","tid":1301041,"uid":273803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6bf095f1fe718412eef01f6a27907d4565467f6f","tid":1301041,"uid":6833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T07:10:00.000Z","msg":"全部保皇狗?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T08:47:33.000Z","msg":"就係得 3 個民主派區議員<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xvUUgiH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxvUUgiH.png&h=7fb61f38&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"50876cdf0cf3474079c66a9279059badd4a7f90c","tid":1301041,"uid":273803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T11:41:52.000Z","msg":"已寫分工，明天 1 點集合，<br />\n大家入嚟報名，我要最少 30 人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nTG group <a href=\"https://t.me/ytm_dc711\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fytm_dc711&d=aELkmJ%2FgRhSQUMA2B8lhBMsFuFiCHHua96MUfZSGoRU%3D&h=9844d178\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/ytm_dc711</a><br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n【旺角政府合署視察】<br />\n<br />\n【圖 1-3】入去之前梗係買支 #運動指定飲品 寶礦力先啦。旺角火車站平台，A 出口旁邊，就係旺角政府合署正門，入去上扶手電梯上 M/F 電梯大堂。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oONKEun.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoONKEun.jpg&h=3ef7c92b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8X9tmHJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8X9tmHJ.jpg&h=a0cdd758&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hOsnq9o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhOsnq9o.jpg&h=b363a55b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【圖 4】4 樓一出 lift 係會議室正門，當日有會議的話，呢個位會做旁聽登記，再行入去。留意，油尖旺區議會 #旁聽席不設預約，聽日開會前大概 1 小時接受即場排隊登記，入面會有大概 30 個位。聽日可能會有藍絲鬥霸位，分工入 Group 再講。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tAXFXf4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtAXFXf4.jpg&h=46d15ce3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【圖5-6】登記處轉左，上面有盞燈度門就係會議室後門。正常登記完就可以在正門行入去。如果太多人想聽嘅話就&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cDM7Cf4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcDM7Cf4.jpg&h=2cd8149c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OnyFcPq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOnyFcPq.jpg&h=19e026f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【圖7-8】後樓梯有兩條，分別係登記處斜對面、電梯大堂另一邊。4 部 lift，兩條樓梯，照計無第 3 類出入口。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qYhOmHL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqYhOmHL.jpg&h=f84ed5d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zpJBvA6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzpJBvA6.jpg&h=f27ee65c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【圖9-14】後樓梯落到 M/F 就係電梯大堂，再落到 G/F 就係大樓後門，通常倒垃圾至會開；同時有個入口入返火車站 A 出口。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K6XyxPs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK6XyxPs.jpg&h=f6a818db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ljaz1HO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLjaz1HO.jpg&h=b7e2dc34&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WwTehga.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWwTehga.jpg&h=2872fc9c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/toSnq9v.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtoSnq9v.jpg&h=379fb217&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ofSq8nR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FofSq8nR.jpg&h=ad2ee30a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WsDBvBc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWsDBvBc.jpg&h=f8509068&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"100cd4f0540df0e1ab7e89e19809a02db999c99d","tid":1301041,"uid":209225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T15:18:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e56b68093e9a635a4b1b5aaa7b006d4e96c020c6","tid":1301041,"uid":209225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T15:23:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c950ea8deced37b3785dc0695c2d435386714867","tid":1301041,"uid":209225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T15:38:04.000Z","msg":"推"}]}